## 📊 KARİYER YOLLARI (HYBRID ERA)

### TRADITIONAL → AI-ENHANCED TRANSFORMATION

#### 1. SOC Analyst → AI Security Orchestrator
- 5 Yıl Sonrası: AI-powered threat detection (60-90K TL/ay)
- 10 Yıl Sonrası: CISO + AI strategy (180-300K TL/ay)
- Transformation: Manual analysis → AI insights management

#### 2. Penetration Tester → AI-Human Hybrid Specialist
- 5 Yıl Sonrası: AI-assisted pentesting (70-110K TL/ay)
- 10 Yıl Sonrası: AI Security R&D Lead (150-280K TL/ay)
- Transformation: Manual testing → AI tool orchestration

#### 3. Security Architect → Strategic AI Security Leader
- 5 Yıl Sonrası: Enterprise AI security (80-130K TL/ay)
- 10 Yıl Sonrası: Chief AI Security Officer (200-350K TL/ay)
- Transformation: Technical design → Strategic AI integration

